Aaaand if you look to your right you’ll see a rippin’ hot new investigation about our nation’s hallowed aviation system. Since the christening of the year, headlines about planes have been popping up everywhere. It got to the point where Dan had no other choice but to hit the tarmac, step in front of a commercial 747, look it dead in the eye and say, “what’s going on here, buster?”
